{"word":"H8181 - שֵׂעָר - sêʻâr - say-awr' - Hair","slug":"H8181","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שֵׂעָר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sêʻâr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>say-awr'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hair"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05E2;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05E2;&#x05E8; - s&#x0301;e&#x0302;&#x201B;a&#x0302;r  s&#x0301;a&#x201B;ar</b> - <i>say-awr', sah'-ar</i><p/>(The second form used in <a href='B:290 7:20'>Isa 7:20</a>); from <a href=\"#/H8175\">H8175</a> in the sense of <i>dishevelling</i>; <i>hair</i> (as if <i>tossed</i> or <i>bristling</i>): - hair (-y), X rough."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8163\">H8163</a>, <a href=\"#/H8165\">H8165</a>, <a href=\"#/H8166\">H8166</a>, <a href=\"#/H8167\">H8167</a>, <a href=\"#/H8175\">H8175</a>, <a href=\"#/H8178\">H8178</a>, <a href=\"#/H8184\">H8184</a>, <a href=\"#/H8185\">H8185</a>, <a href=\"#/H8188\">H8188</a>"}]}